Two.

00:31:30.275 --> 00:31:30.775
One.

00:31:30.916 --> 00:31:32.075
Got it in five seconds?

00:31:32.156 --> 00:31:34.156
Yes. The logic is solid.

00:31:34.315 --> 00:31:35.436
Key legal relationships

00:31:35.436 --> 00:31:36.436
are clearly presented.

00:31:36.436 --> 00:31:38.396
The chart simplifies complex points.

00:31:38.475 --> 00:31:39.075
Perfect.

00:31:40.196 --> 00:31:40.956
Ms. Bai's task?

00:31:43.116 --> 00:31:44.715
No, she criticized my work.

00:31:44.876 --> 00:31:46.315
Said I never consider

00:31:46.315 --> 00:31:47.596
senior attorneys during tasks.

00:31:47.916 --> 00:31:49.116
So from now on,

00:31:49.116 --> 00:31:50.715
I'll think one step ahead on every task.

00:31:50.956 --> 00:31:52.475
You don't understand this case,

00:31:52.475 --> 00:31:53.676
but you grasped it in seconds.

00:31:53.676 --> 00:31:55.475
Meaning any judge would understand too.

00:31:56.995 --> 00:31:58.515
You're becoming Ms. Bai's mini-me.

00:31:59.275 --> 00:32:00.795
Friendly advice though,

00:32:01.075 --> 00:32:02.515
don't worship idols blindly.

00:32:03.436 --> 00:32:05.035
My dad told me

00:32:05.116 --> 00:32:06.555
idols are meant to be humanized.

00:32:06.715 --> 00:32:07.215
Humans

00:32:07.795 --> 00:32:08.515
have flaws.

00:32:08.916 --> 00:32:10.876
Never stop thinking independently.

00:32:12.515 --> 00:32:13.356
Thanks, Mr. Jiang.

00:32:13.916 --> 00:32:15.275
But I need her to notice me first.

00:32:17.235 --> 00:32:17.956
Let's grab dinner.

00:32:18.475 --> 00:32:19.475
I've got a briefing soon.

00:32:20.475 --> 00:32:21.356
Don't say no yet.

00:32:22.555 --> 00:32:23.956
Seriously, thank you.

00:32:24.075 --> 00:32:26.356
You got my dad and me to share a meal.

00:32:27.396 --> 00:32:28.596
It healed something in me.

00:32:29.356 --> 00:32:30.876
Let me return the favor.

00:32:31.116 --> 00:32:31.616
Deal?

00:32:37.836 --> 00:32:38.596
Hello.

00:32:39.075 --> 00:32:41.475
Someone promised coffee. Where is it?

00:32:43.676 --> 00:32:45.836
And I definitely heard a dinner offer.

00:32:46.196 --> 00:32:47.235
How'd you hear that?

00:32:48.555 --> 00:32:49.396
So it's real?

00:32:50.636 --> 00:32:52.196
Yes, a group dinner with everyone.

00:32:52.196 --> 00:32:53.636
Get Li Ke and Yan Fei too.

00:32:53.836 --> 00:32:55.715
Okay, get Yue too.

00:32:55.715 --> 00:32:57.235
She's wedding dress shopping nearby.

00:32:57.995 --> 00:32:59.876
Want to invite Mr. Zhuang?

00:32:59.876 --> 00:33:00.636
Walk to his office,

00:33:00.636 --> 00:33:01.555
knock on his door,

00:33:01.555 --> 00:33:02.235
and tell him.

00:33:05.636 --> 00:33:06.136
Well?

00:33:06.755 --> 00:33:07.596
Go ahead without me.

00:33:07.596 --> 00:33:08.715
I'll catch up later.

00:33:08.995 --> 00:33:09.495
Okay.

00:33:09.795 --> 00:33:10.295
Do come.

00:33:11.596 --> 00:33:13.235
Finally got my coffee. Thanks.

00:33:13.356 --> 00:33:14.676
How did you actually hear us?

00:33:14.956 --> 00:33:16.075
Let me try your seat.

00:33:18.715 --> 00:33:19.215
Thanks.

00:33:19.636 --> 00:33:20.836
Didn't expect you to come.

00:33:22.235 --> 00:33:24.396
I've been pulling nonstop shifts
at the firm.

00:33:24.396 --> 00:33:25.475
I needed a ride.

00:33:26.116 --> 00:33:27.836
My overtime feels like

00:33:27.876 --> 00:33:29.315
another lifetime ago.

00:33:29.636 --> 00:33:31.396
I lost hair daily
from anxiety back then.

00:33:32.196 --> 00:33:33.836
Now that I've heard you say it,

00:33:34.035 --> 00:33:35.715
I actually feel nostalgic
for those days.

00:33:36.515 --> 00:33:37.876
When's the wedding date?

00:33:39.275 --> 00:33:40.356
We're still picking a date.

00:33:40.836 --> 00:33:41.795
If things go well,

00:33:42.116 --> 00:33:42.795
it's next month.

00:33:43.676 --> 00:33:44.715
Congratulations.

00:33:48.555 --> 00:33:50.356
What's that look for?

00:33:53.475 --> 00:33:54.515
How do I put this?

00:33:55.555 --> 00:33:56.356
In theory,

00:33:56.596 --> 00:33:58.555
I've finally achieved
everything I wanted.

00:33:59.755 --> 00:34:02.356
But I feel an emptiness inside.

00:34:03.836 --> 00:34:04.876
It just seems

00:34:05.116 --> 00:34:06.555
all this was what I once

00:34:06.555 --> 00:34:07.795
exhausted myself pursuing.

00:34:08.475 --> 00:34:11.155
Like being perfectly cared for by a man,

00:34:11.555 --> 00:34:13.155
following his schedule every day,

00:34:13.155 --> 00:34:14.396
and learning how to be a wife.

00:34:14.796 --> 00:34:16.916
But being fully supported like that,

00:34:16.995 --> 00:34:17.876
over time,

00:34:18.115 --> 00:34:19.956
it felt like my feet
weren't on the ground.

00:34:20.396 --> 00:34:21.756
Then one day I started panicking.

00:34:23.115 --> 00:34:24.396
The loss of control?

00:34:25.075 --> 00:34:25.575
Exactly.

00:34:25.756 --> 00:34:26.675
That's the feeling.

00:34:28.836 --> 00:34:29.675
I got scared.

00:34:30.475 --> 00:34:32.436
I'm afraid marriage
will erode our love over time

00:34:32.756 --> 00:34:34.716
and wear away my ambition
and professional skills.

00:34:35.035 --> 00:34:36.796
Until I completely lose myself.

00:34:37.276 --> 00:34:39.035
Then wherever he goes,
I'd have to follow.

00:34:39.995 --> 00:34:42.155
He's even planned out
my pregnancy timeline.

00:34:42.956 --> 00:34:44.236
I'm only in my twenties.

00:34:44.675 --> 00:34:45.716
My whole future life

00:34:45.956 --> 00:34:47.356
would revolve around him and kids.

00:34:47.716 --> 00:34:48.555
I'd have no career,

00:34:48.716 --> 00:34:50.035
no social life, and no friends.

00:34:50.195 --> 00:34:50.956
If anything

00:34:50.956 --> 00:34:52.515
ever happens to us,

00:34:52.916 --> 00:34:54.475
I could lose everything.

00:34:59.916 --> 00:35:01.316
Am I being overly dramatic?

00:35:02.436 --> 00:35:03.195
Not at all.

00:35:04.236 --> 00:35:06.195
When going through
such drastic life changes,

00:35:06.195 --> 00:35:08.155
emotional ups and downs
are completely normal.

00:35:08.475 --> 00:35:09.956
Besides, nobody says

00:35:09.956 --> 00:35:11.396
a housewife's life

00:35:11.396 --> 00:35:12.956
can't include friends or social events.

00:35:15.236 --> 00:35:15.796
Good point.

00:35:16.396 --> 00:35:17.635
Looking back now,

00:35:18.236 --> 00:35:19.916
the reason I chose him back then

00:35:20.595 --> 00:35:22.756
was because I'd chased
this lifestyle for too long.

00:35:23.075 --> 00:35:24.356
When he handed it to me,

00:35:24.555 --> 00:35:25.396
I couldn't say no.

00:35:27.236 --> 00:35:27.916
Also,

00:35:28.356 --> 00:35:29.956
maybe beyond socializing and friends,

00:35:31.515 --> 00:35:32.555
I need colleagues too.

00:35:35.595 --> 00:35:37.635
Being a wealthy wife
isn't exactly stress-free.

00:35:38.075 --> 00:35:40.635
But you should protect yourself legally
before marriage.

00:35:40.716 --> 00:35:41.916
Think about that.

00:35:42.716 --> 00:35:44.236
Don't just focus on negative examples.

00:35:44.396 --> 00:35:45.436
Plenty of wives thrive.

00:35:45.916 --> 00:35:47.236
Let's take my mom for instance.

00:35:47.276 --> 00:35:48.675
Spoiled by my dad her whole life.

00:35:48.756 --> 00:35:50.396
Now doted on by my brother.

00:35:50.436 --> 00:35:51.916
She never worked a day.

00:35:52.155 --> 00:35:53.475
Even in her sixties now,

00:35:53.595 --> 00:35:55.436
she's still youthful as ever.

00:35:56.236 --> 00:35:57.956
So when you're that fortunate,

00:35:58.115 --> 00:35:58.916
it's quite good.

00:35:59.396 --> 00:36:01.035
In the long run,

00:36:01.236 --> 00:36:03.515
marriages survive
on mutual respect and conscience.

00:36:03.916 --> 00:36:05.595
Your current panic

00:36:05.635 --> 00:36:06.956
is mostly in your head.

00:36:09.796 --> 00:36:11.035
You haven't changed at all.

00:36:12.595 --> 00:36:13.876
I'll take that as a compliment.

00:36:20.827 --> 00:36:22.876
(Noodles)

00:36:22.876 --> 00:36:23.376
Ma'am,

00:36:23.675 --> 00:36:25.075
any more trouble here lately?

00:36:26.035 --> 00:36:27.195
All quiet now.

00:36:28.075 --> 00:36:28.575
Okay.

