Slow down.

00:36:34.876 --> 00:36:35.876
It's rare to relax.

00:36:36.035 --> 00:36:36.756
Got work to do.

00:36:36.756 --> 00:36:37.396
I need to go.

00:36:37.675 --> 00:36:38.276
Going back?

00:36:50.756 --> 00:36:51.436
I can't wait.

00:36:51.956 --> 00:36:52.595
Maybe next time.

00:36:53.115 --> 00:36:53.615
Leaving now?

00:36:53.995 --> 00:36:54.495
Bye.

