00:37:30.836 --> 00:37:31.716
as the repair fee.

00:37:32.276 --> 00:37:32.776
Thank you.

00:37:32.796 --> 00:37:33.296
Followers,

00:37:33.675 --> 00:37:35.276
the management is twisting the facts.

00:37:35.475 --> 00:37:38.276
They're falsely labeling renovations
as damage.

