Legally,

00:37:39.236 --> 00:37:41.075
when the lessee, who is the shop owner,

00:37:41.475 --> 00:37:43.635
adds attachments to the property,

00:37:43.716 --> 00:37:45.115
they must get the lessor's consent.

00:37:45.316 --> 00:37:46.555
Upon contract termination,

00:37:46.635 --> 00:37:48.316
